Arouna Story # 4 (4/4) - The School
<b> ... In Mali Arouna could live, work, make friends, have a satisfied life. He decided to share his knowlegde with others and founded a school. A rural free school for the kids of the village, where they could learn to read and to write, to produce their own food and make good and sustainable agriculture.. Here you can see the Arouna pupils.. His school is still going...<b></b></b>      The man with the yellow shirt is the Arouna assistant. Years before he was one of his students...
